<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czü Türssenrewt, darumb
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir den Sebach,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan>, cze rede gesaczt und
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er das gelt czü Pernaw mit
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> behabt und <expan>gewunne<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        hab, und maint darumb <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü ew <expan>cze
                                kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> nicht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> man lazz in bey
                            <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und wir getrawen ew wol, war czü
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> unser recht hab, ir seit <add>im</add>
                        dar czü <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>; wan wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und dienst
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Tyb<ex>ur</ex>cii</expan> etc.</ab>
